I fixed the bug in my extreme level by removing the offending wave.

In other news, I finished my first original level.  I am not quite 
happy about 1 thing, though.  How do I get the generators to generate 
monsters faster?  When I was playing the level (with illegimate
team), 
I did not see any signs that the generators were actually doing 
anything.  How much free space do I need around a generator for it to 
work, if any?

If anyone wants to test it, let me know and I will update it.  
Otherwise, I will just upload the whole thing at once and hope they 
are not too tough.
